{"tid":1865001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"袁國勇稱警隊可協助調查被隔離人士","createTime":"2020-02-06T02:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T05:56:57.000Z","uid":212626,"like":657,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"3dd9a225bef0997fc68d27b118dbbf0717eb6195","tid":1865001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:42:09.000Z","msg":"港大微生物系講座教授袁國勇接受本台節目《千禧年代》電話訪問時表示，新型肺炎個案愈來愈多，當局應該盡量找合適的隔離設施。袁國勇以「世界夢號」郵輪約有2000人需要隔離為例，指由於無法找到足夠宿位，因此一定要在船上隔離，政府亦可能需要考慮會否在碼頭設立大量帳幕。<br />\n<br />\n對於星期六起從內地入境的人士需要強制檢疫14天，袁國勇表示，在沒有足夠隔離設施下，唯有在家居隔離，衞生署醫生需要上門視察環境和給予建議，例如被隔離人士的家人都需要戴口罩，以及分房用膳等。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，每座大廈和附近商戶都有閉路電視，警察可以抽樣調查，如果發現有人離開住所，就需要罰款甚至坐監，給予一定阻嚇作用，最重要是衞生署和警察是否有意志執行嚴厲措施，否則強制隔離就沒有效果。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506963-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506963-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=c695e763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506963-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=804f5673\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506963-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"d8a363968412322d63f994fe562a7ba65f258caa","tid":1865001,"uid":108347,"like":129,"dislike":0,"score":129,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:42:58.000Z","msg":"真個D佢唔會查,反而會特登攪手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b797b975b5d259fc3bf1138d0c5ed269b96e6f06","tid":1865001,"uid":48889,"like":131,"dislike":0,"score":131,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:43:45.000Z","msg":"根本呢啲先係狗嘅職責嚟"},{"pid":"41b1766b6b17a26bae6bc3b1b3d9167e8e4df8c8","tid":1865001,"uid":132999,"like":47,"dislike":0,"score":47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:44:56.0