&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mcWmDvg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmcWmDvg.png&h=bd5829bf&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e0097234f1f77de0cdedc7f919f9040684781aab","tid":1865001,"uid":46534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T04:51:43.000Z","msg":"班懦夫唔會查架"},{"pid":"f6dbc28efcbadb525f2eea40ed282cc65db615e8","tid":1865001,"uid":56381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e1f540b8857f7e1281eae01ba969a3bbc3c56fe","tid":1865001,"uid":326037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3dd9a225bef0997fc68d27b118dbbf0717eb6195","tid":1865001,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T02:42:09.000Z","msg":"港大微生物系講座教授袁國勇接受本台節目《千禧年代》電話訪問時表示，新型肺炎個案愈來愈多，當局應該盡量找合適的隔離設施。袁國勇以「世界夢號」郵輪約有2000人需要隔離為例，指由於無法找到足夠宿位，因此一定要在船上隔離，政府亦可能需要考慮會否在碼頭設立大量帳幕。<br />\n<br />\n對於星期六起從內地入境的人士需要強制檢疫14天，袁國勇表示，在沒有足夠隔離設施下，唯有在家居隔離，衞生署醫生需要上門視察環境和給予建議，例如被隔離人士的家人都需要戴口罩，以及分房用膳等。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，每座大廈和附近商戶都有閉路電視，警察可以抽樣調查，如果發現有人離開住所，就需要罰款甚至坐監，給予一定阻嚇作用，最重要是衞生署和警察是否有意志執行嚴厲措施，否則強制隔離就沒有效果。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506963-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506963-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=N89%2BOK2GKuUyahfhaKnAsq3e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=c695e763\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506963-20200206.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=804f5673\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506963-20200206.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T05:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y5iXbWB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy5iXbWB.png&h=a953f965&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f25